mappingId	mapping--1604254561
target		<http://example.com/fclpoint/{fclnpdidfacility}> <http://sws.ifi.uio.no/vocab/npd-v2#dateStatusFrom> {fclstartupdate}^^xsd:dateTime ; <http://sws.ifi.uio.no/vocab/npd-v2#waterDepth> {fclwaterdepth}^^xsd:decimal ; <http://sws.ifi.uio.no/vocab/npd-v2#coresTotalLength> {fclbelongstos}^^xsd:decimal ; <http://sws.ifi.uio.no/vocab/npd-v2#facilityFunction> {fclfunctions}^^xsd:string ; <http://sws.ifi.uio.no/vocab/npd-v2#name> {fclname}^^xsd:string ; <http://sws.ifi.uio.no/vocab/npd-v2#designLifetime> {fcldesignlifetime}^^xsd:integer . 
