mappingId	mapping--525642864
target		<http://example.com/licence/{prlnpdidlicence}> a <http://sws.ifi.uio.no/vocab/npd-v2#ProductionLicence> ; <http://sws.ifi.uio.no/vocab/npd-v2#dateLicenceGranted> {ptldatevalidto}^^xsd:dateTime , {ptldatevalidfrom}^^xsd:dateTime ; <http://sws.ifi.uio.no/vocab/npd-v2-ptl#dateAwarded> {ptldateawarded}^^xsd:dateTime ; <http://sws.ifi.uio.no/vocab/npd-v2#dateSyncNPD> {datesyncnpd}^^xsd:dateTime ; <http://sws.ifi.uio.no/vocab/npd-v2#datesyncnpd> {datesyncnpd}^^xsd:dateTime ; <http://sws.ifi.uio.no/vocab/npd-v2#dateUpdated> {ptldateupdated}^^xsd:dateTime ; <http://sws.ifi.uio.no/vocab/npd-v2#name> {ptlname}^^xsd:string ; <http://sws.ifi.uio.no/vocab/npd-v2#dateUpdatedMax> {ptldateupdatedmax}^^xsd:dateTime . 
